Package: ph2bayes
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Single-Arm Phase II Designs
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
  person("Kengo", "Nagashima", email = "nshi1201@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4529-9045"))
Description: An implementation of Bayesian single-arm phase II design methods for binary outcome based on posterior
  probability (Thall and Simon (1994) <doi:10.2307/2533377>) and predictive probability (Lee and Liu (2008) <doi:10.1177/1740774508089279>).
